heroku keys(prints all keys)
ssh -v git@heroku.com(communicating with heroku server)
make two changes ,heroku does most of the things automatically

make a port dynamic as we have to make an environment variable so that node can read that port while heroku is running

to check all the environment variable :SET command in terminal


